===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A triangular steel structure incorporated into or attached to the bow of a [[pushboat]]; allows the boat to face up to a [[barge]] which is higher than the deck of the pushboat.
#:''The deckhand had to climb the pushknee to get onto the empty barge.''

